
  KEY			ACTION				    KEY			ACTION
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

		  WM							  GAPS
  Mod+Shift+R		Reload configs			    Mod+O		Plus outer gaps 
  Mod+Shift+E		Exit				    Mod+Shift+O		Minus outer gaps
  Mod+Shift+W		Toggle composite		    Mod+I		Plus inner gaps
			manager				    Mod+Shift+I		Minus inner gaps
  Mod+Shift+M		Connect second monitor		    Mod+Shift+G		Set gaps to default
							    Mod+G		Remove gaps
  		LAUNCH					    
  Mod+Enter		Start terminal					  MODES
  Mod+B			Start Luakit			    Mod+Shift+resize	Set mode to resize
  Mod+Shift+B		Start Chromium			    Mod+Shift+C		Set mode to cmus
  Mod+D			Start dmenu			    Mod+Shift+P		Set mode to MPD
							    Escape or Space	Exit from any mode
		WINDOWS						       
  Mod+Shift+Q		Close window			    		RESIZE MODE
  Mod+{ARROW}		Focus {ARROW}			    h or Left		Shrink width to 10px
  Mod+Shift+{ARROW}	Move window {ARROW}		    j or Down		Grow height to 10px
  Mod+H			Horizontal orientation		    k or Up		Shrink height to 10px
  Mod+V			Vertical orientation		    l or Right		Grow width to 10px
  Mod+F			Toggle fullscreen			    
  Mod+W			Change layout to stacked	   	    CMUS OR MPD MODE 
  Mod+W			Change layout to tabbed		    Right or n		Next track
  Mod+Shift+Space	Toggle tiling/floating  	    Left  or u		Previous track
  Mod+Space		Toggle focus to			    Space or p		Toggle pause
			tiling/floating windows		    Up			Grow volume to 2
  Mod+A			Focus parent container		    Down		Shrink volume to 2
  Mod+1..0		Move to workspace		    R			Toggle repeat current
  Mod+Shift+1..0	Move window to workspace	    a or h		Rewind -5 seconds 
  Mod+T			Toggle borders for window	    d or l		Rewind +5 seconds

		 TOOLS

  Mod+S			Take a screenshot
  Mod+U			Toggle Unified Remote Daemon
  Mod+L			Lock
  Mod+Shift+L		Lock and suspend
